OL,6,FIn the last four years, the housing
OL,7,Fbody has had three prevention of
OL,8,Ffuture death reports.
OL,10,FA prevention of future death report
OL,11,Fprovides coroners with the duty to
OL,12,Fmake reports to a person,
OL,13,Forganisation, local authority or
OL,14,Fgovernment department or agency where
OL,15,Fthe coroner believes that action
OL,16,Fshould be taken to prevent future
OL,17,Fdeaths.
OL,19,FOne of those was after the death of
OL,20,Ffive year old Malika Hibu.
