OL,3,CHousing association tops London list
OL,4,Cof prevention of future death orders
OL,6,FMalika fell into a canal and drowned
OL,7,Fin February 2024. She opened the door
OL,8,Fof her home at Crest Buildings, Wharf
OL,9,FRoad and ran towards the canal before
OL,10,Fshe fell in. She was found 25 minutes
OL,11,Flater, and was pronounced dead at St.
OL,12,FThomas' hospital.
OL,14,FAn inquest into her death found that
OL,15,FPeabody had failed to act on
OL,16,Fcomplaints that the nearby barrier
OL,17,Fwasn't safe, they had not carried out
OL,18,Fa risk assessment of the land and had
OL,19,Fnot realised that land belonged to
OL,20,Fthem.
