OL,6,FHer dad, Mohammed Hibu, says he
OL,7,Fbelieves Peabody are "one hundred per
OL,8,Fcent" to blame for Malika's death.
OL,10,FHe said: "They totally ignored
OL,11,Fpeople's warnings, so as a result, I
OL,12,Fpaid my beloved daughter. She fell
OL,13,Fdown here, she passed away.
OL,15,F"This is Peabody's land, Peabody's
OL,16,Festate....when they built the estate
OL,17,Fthey didn't assess (the) risk."
OL,19,FHowever, Peabody have responded to Mr
OL,20,FHibu's allegations.
