OL,6,F"The coroner's report into what
OL,7,Fhappened is wide-ranging and
OL,8,Fpotentially raises serious questions
OL,9,Fabout the safety of families across
OL,10,Fthe country who live near water and
OL,11,Fother hazards. It also raises
OL,12,Fquestions about the responsibility of
OL,13,Flandlords when it comes to personal
OL,14,Fsafety.
OL,16,F"As part of our original planning
OL,17,Fconsent, we were not allowed to have
OL,18,Fany kind of barrier to the canal.
