OL,6,FIn 2016, Elizabeth was moved two
OL,7,Fstreets away from her daughter, Tina,
OL,8,Finto a warden assisted block. Tina
OL,9,Ftold Peabody to tell support stuff to
OL,10,Flet her know if anything happened to
OL,11,Fher mother.
OL,13,FTina described the housing as only
OL,14,F"five minutes away" which was
OL,15,Fimportant as her mother's health was
OL,16,Fdeteriorating.
OL,18,FIn August 2020, Elizabeth suffered a
OL,19,Ffall. Support staff helped her back to
OL,20,Fher feet but they did not contact Tina.
