OL,6,FLater that day, she fell again and was
OL,7,Flaying on the floor for hours. She
OL,8,Flater died in hospital from pneumonia.
OL,10,F"I do believe if Peabody contacted me
OL,11,Fafter that first fall, she would still
OL,12,Fbe alive," said Tina.
OL,14,F"I would have stayed with her or
OL,15,Fbrought her back over here and she
OL,16,Fwouldn't have been left alone if she
OL,17,Fwas in a distressed state so yeah, I
OL,18,Fdo believe she would have been alive."
