OL,6,FIn response, Peabody have said: "We
OL,7,Fhave received three prevention of
OL,8,Ffuture death reports over the last
OL,9,Ffour years. We reviewed the
OL,10,Frecommendations on a case-by-case
OL,11,Fbasis, including after the very sad
OL,12,Fdeath of Mrs. Pamment. Where possible
OL,13,Fwe've acted on these and made
OL,14,Fimprovements to our processes or
OL,15,Fservices."
OL,17,FThe Housing Ombudsman added:
OL,18,F"Coroner's reports can be extremely
OL,19,Fimportant.
